description:
The Garden of Eden is a magical land that stands apart as the most magnificent and mysterious place in all of history. Join me as we dive into the astonishing details of this extraordinary land. Where was the garden of Eden located? What were the trees, land, and sky like? How did Adam and Eve spend their days in this garden paradise? How did the creatures of the garden interact with the first humans? Will the Garden of Eden be recreated someday? If so, how can you witness that spectacular event?!
